應\r\n附繕本）\r\n                               書記官  張雅如\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　2 　　月　　25　　日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCDM/111%2c%e5%96%ae%e7%a6%81%e6%b2%92%2c207%2c20220224%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TCDM,111,單禁沒,207,20220224,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"單禁沒","JNO":"207","JDATE":"20220224","JTITLE":"聲請單獨宣告沒收"}